include ./components/_card
include ./components/_banner

doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="IE=edge")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Curso Responsive Web Design EDteam
    link(rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com")
    link(href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="./styles/style.css")

  body 
    //- Header
    header.main-header 
      .l-container.main-header__block
        img(src="./resources/img/EDteam-logo.svg", alt="Logo EDteam" class="main-header__logo")
        .main-menu-toggle#main-menu-toggle
        nav.main-nav#main-nav
          ul.main-menu
            li.main-menu__item: a(href="#").main-menu__link Taller de emprendedores
            li.main-menu__item: a(href="#").main-menu__link Workshops
            li.main-menu__item: a(href="#").main-menu__link Expositores
            
    //- Main banner
    +banner 

    //- Main
    main
      //- Descripcion
      section.l-section
        .l-container
          p.s-50.l-50.center-block.center-content
            | El EDcamp es el evento internacional de tecnologia de EDteam. Dos dias para compartir conocimientos, experiencias y crecer profesionalmente. El staff de EDteam completo por primera vez en Lima. Te esperamos!
      //- Eventos
      section.l-section.l-section--diagonal
        .l-container
          h2.s-100.l-100.center-content Eventos 
          .card-grid
            +card
            +card
      //- Expositores
      section.l-section
      //- Ediciones anteriores
      section.lsection.l-section--diagonal
      //- Inscripciones
      section.l-section
    //- Footer
    footer.main-footer
    script(src="./js/index.js") 